###Step 1 :: Download the RPM Package
wget https://github.com/cli/cli/releases/download/v2.15.0/gh_2.15.0_linux_amd64.rpm

###Step 2 :: Install the package
sudo rpm -i gh_2.15.0_linux_amd64.rpm

###Step 3 :: Now check the github cli version
gh --version

Note :: First find out if you are using a 32 bit OS or a 64 but OS. For 32 bit OS use below commands...

wget https://github.com/cli/cli/releases/download/v2.15.0/gh_2.15.0_linux_386.rpm
sudo rpm -i gh_2.15.0_linux_386.rpm
